{"tid":2515212,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"地球上又多一個女富豪","createTime":"2021-05-03T21:56:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T23:39:43.000Z","uid":388176,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a612ae48613cdeec90157490136fbb3dcd634a2e","tid":2515212,"uid":388176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T21:56:53.000Z","msg":"<strong>蓋茨夫婦宣布離婚 結束27年婚姻</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUv6go3PesFioes6jU6fsDXwc89bdtXTRVziEXqnbnXJ3?filename=FNJtFfb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFNJtFfb.jpg&h=1112c36b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n微軟共同創辦人蓋茨(Bill Gates)與妻子梅林達(Melinda)宣布離婚，結束長達27年的婚姻關係。聲明稱他們將繼續在基金會一起工作。<br />\n蓋茨在社交媒體發表聲明稱，經過一番深思熟慮及理順雙方關係後，與妻子決定結束二人的婚姻關係。聲明指「2人相信再不能作為一對夫婦成長」。<br />\n據美國《福布斯》本年度全球富豪榜，蓋茲以淨資產1240億美元排名第4。"},{"pid":"5f66e1b486294ed9e3caa21b554fac127c993d15","tid":2515212,"uid":82752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T22:55:22.000Z","msg":"缺男朋友嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d18e7fcdb17a971fd60c6b260a77b6c0571416b","tid":2515212,"uid":261587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:00:53.000Z","msg":"做左咁耐ptbf，今鋪我仲唔飛上枝頭變利基亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32d429a2af71099363ff832078626e9e4f7e0040","tid":2515212,"uid":170249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d18e7fcdb17a971fd60c6b260a77b6c0571416b","tid":2515212,"uid":261587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:00:53.000Z","msg":"做左咁耐ptbf，今鋪我仲唔飛上枝頭變利基亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T23:39:43.000Z","msg":"龜頭變雞頭就有你份"}]}